{"type":null,"faqId":48085,"title":"用 PIN 码保护 SIM 卡","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>PIN 码是随 SIM 卡一起提供的个人身份识别码。您可以开启 SIM 卡的PIN 码保护，开启后，每次开机时都需要正确输入 SIM 卡的 PIN 码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"PIN码\"XE \"PIN码保护\"XE \"SIM卡保护\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在执行以下操作前，请确保您已经从网络运营商处获取了 SIM 卡的 PIN 码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178138\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“安全”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>点击“设置 卡槽一/卡槽二 卡锁”或“设置 卡 1/卡 2 卡锁”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4.  </span><span>点击“锁定 SIM 卡”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">5.  </span><span>输入 PIN 码，然后点击“确定”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">6.  </span><span>点击“修改 SIM 卡 PIN 码”，可以修改 SIM 卡的PIN码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178139\" style=\"width:0.93680555in;height:0.43680555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>在错误输入 PIN 码的次数达到最大限制次数后，需要输入 PUK 码进行解锁。如果错误输入 PUK 码的次数达到最大限制次数，SIM 卡将作废。PIN 码和 PUK 码的最大限制次数请咨询网络运营商。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3671","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598115000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":92,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}